longBusinessSummary: PreCheck Health Services, Inc. distributes medical screening device in the United States. It offers PC8B medical device, a screening tool designed for use by physicians and medical personnel in managing patient's health. The company was formerly known as Nature's Best Brands, Inc. and changed its name to PPreCheck Health Services, Inc. in January 2019. PreCheck Health Services, Inc. was founded in 2014 and is based in Miami, Florida.
